BIBISH Versioning Scheme

0.0.1 Initial release - Basic commands show, list, quit, help, select.

Development Versioning

0.x.y

Where x is the milestone release as described in the MILESTONES file and
y is the bug fix only release for that milestone.

Stable Versioning

1.x.y

After version 1.0.0 the release is considered "Mature" and versioning will be
as follows, minor releases y are for bug fixes only, major releases x are
reserved for changing to a new SWORD project release.
